list.abstract: CUSTOM日本东洋计量株式会社昭和63年6月20日由佐藤有功社长创立，主要产品有约400款产品（计测，计量，环境计测，生活计测，半导体关联产品，工具关联产品等六大类行业）。

yingyinNormal.en: At said ball, in accordance with ancient custom, the prince shall choose a bride.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在这场舞会上根据传统风俗，王子将会选择他的新娘。

yingyinNormal.en: This custom was later appropriated by Northern Europeans and eventually it becomes the so-called Christmas tree.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这种风俗后来被北欧人继承，于是演变成了现在的圣诞树。

yingyinNormal.en: You know Germans have an interesting pre wedding custom… Well, it's probably not for me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 知道吗？德国人有个有趣的婚前习俗……估计不太适合我吧。

yingyinNormal.en: So Kati mentioned something about a custom-made corset and I hear there are wigs involved?
yingyinNormal.zh: 凯帝提到了高级定制的束胸，我听说她还要戴假发？

yingyinNormal.en: You know? And you don't need this custom-made, empire waist, duchess, satin gown, you can wear off the rack.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你不需要这种订做的帝国式腰线、公主型丝缎礼服，你可以买现成的礼服。

yingyinNormal.en: They had red, beady eyes. They got all in my lovely locks. Oh, I can smell it right now. Total inside custom job.
yingyinNormal.zh: 它们有着红色的大眼，有些还在我的卷发里，我闻得到，完全是客制化的改装！

yingyinNormal.en: Oh they are nice. We custom-make tuxedos for celebrities and then when they're done with them, they just send them back.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是不错，名人穿过这些之后，就送回来这儿。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay. Exactly. Now, which tab do I click on to get different font styles? How many custom typefaces are there on LisaWrite?
yingyinNormal.zh: 好，确切说是这样，现在，我想改变字体的时候点哪个标签呢？“丽萨写作”有多少种自定义字体？

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Perhaps the world's languages, music, social and religious <highlight>customs</highlight> and even history are governed by universal features.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 也许世界上的语言、音乐、社会和宗教习俗，甚至历史都受普遍特征的支配。

examination_example.sentence: In China, it's a traditional <highlight>custom</highlight> to bring a gift when you are invited to someone's home.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在中国，应邀去别人家做客时要带礼物是一个传统习俗。

examination_example.sentence: According to the traditional Chinese <highlight>custom</highlight>, 2018 is just the year of Dog.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 根据中国的传统习俗，2018年正好是狗年。

examination_example.sentence: Since the Western Han Dynasty, it has been the <highlight>custom</highlight> of climbing on the Chongyang Festival.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 自西汉以来，重阳节便有登高的习俗。

examination_example.sentence: Good revision (复习) should give you confidence, but if you are still worried, it’s not harmful to follow some special <highlight>customs</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 认真复习会给你信心，但如果你还是担心，遵循一些特殊的习惯也无妨。
